      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a common challenge when bringing social values into a business, and your customers' concern about neutrality is understandable. You don't need to take a \"hard stance\"; instead, focus on *inclusion* as a core business value, not political activism. Framing DEI as making your space welcoming to *everyone*—regardless of background—is a professional way to communicate commitment without inviting polarizing debate.",
